HOME_DELIVERY.delivery_time: 1-2 business days. Orders placed by 11:00 AM are dispatched the same business day and delivered the next business day.

PARCEL_SHOPS.pricing: 79 Kč. Free for orders over 2 500 Kč.

IN_STORE_PICKUP.pricing: 10,- Kč for orders under 1 500,- Kč. Free for orders of 1 500,- Kč and over.

SUMMARY:
DELIVERY OPTIONS: Freshlabels.cz offers three main delivery methods for Czechia: Home Delivery, Parcel Shops, and In-Store Pickup.
PROVIDERS & PRICING: Home delivery is handled by GLS and DPD, both costing 89 Kč. Parcel shop delivery is via Zásilkovna for 79 Kč and is free for orders over 2,500 Kč. In-store pickup in Prague costs 10 Kč for orders under 1,500 Kč and is free above that amount. A Cash on Delivery (COD) surcharge of 40 Kč applies to shipped orders.
DELIVERY SPEED: Standard delivery is very fast, typically 1-2 business days, with next-day delivery for orders placed before 11:00 AM.
NOTABLE FEATURES: The key feature is the fast standard delivery. Free shipping thresholds differ based on the chosen delivery method. The company does not offer express or weekend delivery services. Delivery to Česká pošta branches is not available.
WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: Shipping information is consolidated on the FAQ page. While generally clear, the structure could be improved to more easily distinguish the terms for each delivery method, particularly regarding the free shipping rules. Information on parcel lockers is not explicitly provided.
